Package com.ibm.itim.apps.jaas.callback Description

Contains implementations of JAAS Callback and CallbackHandler interfaces.

The implementations are used by the remotable Applications API to interact with the underlying authentication services. For a high-level overview, see the Applications API Overview

Related Documentation

For overviews, tutorials, examples, and guides about JAAS see:
  • Java Authentication and Authorization Service
